name: Pseudanabaena sp. PCC 7367
description: The CyanoGEBA Sequencing Project is part of the DOE Joint Genome Institute Genomic Encyclopedia of Bacteria and Archaeainitiative. The CyanoGEBA project is a collaboration between the JGI and the Pasteur Culture Collection aimed at improving sequencing coverage of the cyanobacterial phylum based on phylogenetic criteria.
